text: Eva Lacinová (born 3 October 1971) is a Czech badminton player, born in Prague. She competed in women's singles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Czechoslovakia Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
